THOSE who earned a salary before would know that getting your first salary is a big deal. No matter how long it is since a person has received their first salary, they hardly ever forget the day. Also also what they did with it. Among the trending topics on Twitter today, is people sharing what they did with their first pay.#WhatIDidWithMyFirstSalary. Now a lot of people are sharing their touching, funny and sad stories of what happened to their first pay cheques.. #WhatIDidWithMyFirstSalary i was an intern earning R3500. My daugher was 18 months. I struggled alot with her, being a single mother. I bought 6 packets of pampers amongst other things and it felt sooo good...now shes 11 and im happily married to her dad. Life???? 